                "url": "/topics/i_can"
            },
            {
                "name": "Tell",
                "url": "/topics/tell"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558652",
        "quote": "That's the thing about great artists: They find the thing that's most obvious to themselves, what's most conscious and natural, and they put it out there and the audience comes.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558652"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Audience",
                "url": "/topics/audience"
            },
            {
                "name": "Natural",
                "url": "/topics/natural"
            },
            {
                "name": "About",
                "url": "/topics/about"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558653",
        "quote": "I've never really heard anybody imitating anything of mine the way they do with Edward Van Halen's stuff.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558653"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Mine",
                "url": "/topics/mine"
            },
            {
                "name": "Anybody",
                "url": "/topics/anybody"
            },
            {
                "name": "Van",
                "url": "/topics/van"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558655",
        "quote": "I knew that I was going to have a life as a musician, because I always felt the pull. I don't remember ever having to make a choice.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558655"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Always",
                "url": "/topics/always"
            },
            {
                "name": "Going",
                "url": "/topics/going"
            },
            {
                "name": "Having",
                "url": "/topics/having"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558657",
        "quote": "I didn't have any aspirations of becoming famous or successful; in fact I was scared to death of all that. I remember somebody once said that if a rock musician goes on tour, he goes insane. I was very impressionable and I carried this useless weight of fear around with me about going on tour, all because of this thing somebody said.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558657"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "I Remember",
                "url": "/topics/i_remember"
            },
            {
                "name": "Very",
                "url": "/topics/very"
            },
            {
                "name": "Becoming",
                "url": "/topics/becoming"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558658",
        "quote": "I created this picture of this character who would play the guitar effortlessly, who had no limitations, performing beautiful music, and he moved around with great acrobatic skills, just capturing the audience and being a great entertainer.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558658"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Play",
                "url": "/topics/play"
            },
            {
                "name": "Beautiful Music",
                "url": "/topics/beautiful_music"
            },
            {
                "name": "Moved",
                "url": "/topics/moved"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558659",
        "quote": "I've learned over the years that you're going to be most successful at the things you're most excited to do. Every artist has a special set of tools. When you really use those tools, and you make yourself feel really good about the product you create, I think you'll find an audience for it. I've been very fortunate in that respect.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558659"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "I Think",
                "url": "/topics/i_think"
            },
            {
                "name": "Very",
                "url": "/topics/very"
            },
            {
                "name": "Been",
                "url": "/topics/been"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558660",
        "quote": "I think every artist subconsciously wants to evolve themselves. Sometimes they get stuck in ruts because of pop culture, peer pressure, stuff like that. But what excites me most is exploring my own musical insights and expanding upon them.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558660"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Artist",
                "url": "/topics/artist"
            },
            {
                "name": "I Think",
                "url": "/topics/i_think"
            },
            {
                "name": "Expanding",
                "url": "/topics/expanding"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558661",
        "quote": "I wanted to be a composer before anything else. And my sister was listening to Led Zeppelin in the other room! When I heard that, it was a game-changer.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558661"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Listening",
                "url": "/topics/listening"
            },
            {
                "name": "Before",
                "url": "/topics/before"
            },
            {
                "name": "Other",
                "url": "/topics/other"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558662",
        "quote": "I designed a guitar for Ibanez and then they started manufacturing it - it's called the Jem - it's 26 years old and I still play it. As a kid I liked Les Pauls and Strats, but they had limitations for the kind of playing I wanted to do.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558662"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Play",
                "url": "/topics/play"
            },
            {
                "name": "Kid",
                "url": "/topics/kid"
            },
            {
                "name": "Had",
                "url": "/topics/had"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558663",
        "quote": "I was a kid, 12 or something, when the Partridge Family was big on TV. I liked the curly cord running from the bass to the amps, which were real fancy. That cord looked so cool. I said, 'Wow! I gotta play something like that!'",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558663"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Play",
                "url": "/topics/play"
            },
            {
                "name": "Big",
                "url": "/topics/big"
            },
            {
                "name": "TV",
                "url": "/topics/tv"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558664",
        "quote": "I could never overstate the importance of a musician's need to develop his or her ear. Actually, I believe that developing a good 'inner ear' - the art of being able to decipher musical components solely through listening - is the most important element in becoming a good musician.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558664"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Through",
                "url": "/topics/through"
            },
            {
                "name": "Components",
                "url": "/topics/components"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558665",
        "quote": "Possessing a healthy imagination is a necessary ingredient for creativity.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558665"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Ingredient",
                "url": "/topics/ingredient"
            },
            {
                "name": "Necessary",
                "url": "/topics/necessary"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558666",
        "quote": "All musicians practice ear training constantly, whether or not they are cognizant of it. If, when listening to a piece of music, a musician is envisioning how to play it or is trying to play along, that musician is using his or her 'ear' - the understanding and recognition of musical elements - for guidance.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558666"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Musicians",
                "url": "/topics/musicians"
            },
            {
                "name": "Practice",
                "url": "/topics/practice"
            },
            {
                "name": "Play",
                "url": "/topics/play"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558667",
        "quote": "I've always considered transcribing to be an invaluable tool in the development of one's musical ear and, over the years, I have spent countless glorious hours transcribing different kinds of music, either guitar-oriented or not.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_558667"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Development",
                "url": "/topics/development"
            },
            {
                "name": "Always",
                "url": "/topics/always"
            },
            {
                "name": "Over",
                "url": "/topics/over"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581679",
        "quote": "As a musician, I look for certain things that stimulate me. And what I look for is something that's an evolution on a particular genre that I never heard before.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581679"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Before",
                "url": "/topics/before"
            },
            {
                "name": "Certain Things",
                "url": "/topics/certain_things"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581680",
        "quote": "When I was young, I wasn't a misfit or anything. I had friends in all the different social groups. But I had issues - just personal issues, insecurities and other things that had happened in my life.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581680"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "My Life",
                "url": "/topics/my_life"
            },
            {
                "name": "Young",
                "url": "/topics/young"
            },
            {
                "name": "Other",
                "url": "/topics/other"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581681",
        "quote": "Criticism can be devastating. When push comes to shove, we are all very sensitive.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581681"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Sensitive",
                "url": "/topics/sensitive"
            },
            {
                "name": "Very",
                "url": "/topics/very"
            },
            {
                "name": "Devastating",
                "url": "/topics/devastating"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581682",
        "quote": "I was always one of those guys who was a seeker after truth. I want to know what's going on.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581682"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Want",
                "url": "/topics/want"
            },
            {
                "name": "Always",
                "url": "/topics/always"
            },
            {
                "name": "Going",
                "url": "/topics/going"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581683",
        "quote": "The blues scale was the first thing I learned. It's just a pentatonic scale with a flat seventh and a few notes that sound cool when you bend them. And because people have amalgamated the blues into this rock-blues scale, if you're using it, you better sound like a real authentic blues player.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581683"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Sound",
                "url": "/topics/sound"
            },
            {
                "name": "Notes",
                "url": "/topics/notes"
            },
            {
                "name": "Scale",
                "url": "/topics/scale"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581684",
        "quote": "The older I get, the more I just like plugging directly into my amp. I'm tired of trying to impress myself with weird sounds. It's about the notes more.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581684"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Notes",
                "url": "/topics/notes"
            },
            {
                "name": "Like",
                "url": "/topics/like"
            },
            {
                "name": "Amp",
                "url": "/topics/amp"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581685",
        "quote": "When I was growing up, the blues did seem too simple to me. I was just a muso.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581685"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Simple",
                "url": "/topics/simple"
            },
            {
                "name": "Blues",
                "url": "/topics/blues"
            },
            {
                "name": "Seem",
                "url": "/topics/seem"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581686",
        "quote": "It's very hard to come across as a passionate human being in print. People can't hear the inflections in your voice.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581686"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Voice",
                "url": "/topics/voice"
            },
            {
                "name": "Human Being",
                "url": "/topics/human_being"
            },
            {
                "name": "Very",
                "url": "/topics/very"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581687",
        "quote": "I can tell you this: I'm an extremely passionate individual. I try to be careful how I display it because you never know how people are going to take it.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steve Vai",
            "url": "/quotes/steve_vai_581687"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Passionate",
                "url": "/topics/passionate"
            },
            {
                "name": "Be Careful",
                "url": "/topics/be_careful"
            }
        ]
    }
